[normal]Introduction[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]Aviva 
[normal]is supportive of 
[normal]initiatives that preserve 
[normal]li
[normal]fe or
[normal] prevent injur
[normal]y
[normal]. Aviva 
[normal]is 
[normal]also 
[normal]committed to recognising good 
[normal]standards of 
[normal]risk management and assist
[normal] our
[normal] 
[normal]p
[normal]olicyholders to achieve these goals by 
[normal]employing a 
[normal]nationwide 
[normal]team of 
[normal]Fleet 
[normal]Risk Consultants
[normal]. These individuals help customers to identify 
[normal]key 
[normal]hazards
[normal], 
[normal]then provid
[normal]e
