[normal]Over recent years, Aviva has witnessed a significant rise in the frequency of claims involving cyclists under our Commercial 
[normal]Motor 
[normal]Fleet account, which is up 64% across 2011/12 compared with the 2008-10 average 
[normal](see graph below). 
[normal]It is also apparent in our data, that 
